instruction: Please analyze the May 2020 index turnover within the context of the past May SAIRs exhibited below, taking into account both benign and volatile market environments, and discuss the possible impact of relative market volatility on index-rebalancing turnover.
output: After analyzing the exhibit below, it can be observed that the May 2020 index turnover falls within the range of past May SAIRs. The 12-year period covered in the exhibit includes both benign and volatile market environments, such as the 2008 global financial crisis. Despite the varying market conditions, it can be noted that relative market volatility did not have a significant impact on index-rebalancing turnover.
